{"tid":2410584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緬甸6/2起已經開始運海鮮 上網忽然見到中文字","createTime":"2021-02-16T17:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T06:21:01.000Z","uid":68125,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4a4ed4aaaad1c82707d4766ca5fcfb99c87cc30b","tid":2410584,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T17:40:47.000Z","msg":"以下內容轉自K&rsquo;s Aviation <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1515218445347718/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F495667450636161%2Fposts%2F1515218445347718%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BSWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=398382fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1515218445347718/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G7bPCuC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG7bPCuC.jpg&h=dfbcd21a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼續關心緬甸的國民處境。<br />\n<br />\n昨日提到緬甸國際航空(8M) 近日有不明航班，該等航班主要為來往中國雲南昆明長水機場 (KMG) 。<br />\n<br />\n剷屎官小編循緬甸中國企業商會發出日&mdash;即10/2作為調查起點，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">發現該等航班早於6/2起已經運作，同樣地航班由緬甸國際航空(8M) 之A319及A320營運，直到今日當刻依然正在運作</span></span>，換言之緬甸當局來回中國運海鮮的行動已經維持最少十日。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面緬甸現時連續2晚斷網，於Twitter上<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">除發現當局向用戶發出之SMS外，也有網民指出無使用VPN的情況下使用Youtube會顯示中國網民喜好影片，使用Facebook會顯示中文字及有不明中文字符</span></span>，原因並無交代。"},{"pid":"dd6b907016d8de30dc2ba146eb3be670d7362b57","tid":2410584,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T17:44:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bcdc94b48352e50e0096eff70c31de662b7aefcd","tid":2410584,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T17:50:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e6c94941c03460aa6e1d5ff5d69a47ff384f3ce","tid":2410584,"uid":222224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T17:51:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06f9a1ade3225310ccfc8750c844dedd207bd2e8","tid":2410584,"uid":6812